[/asy]

Since $\angle ABD = \frac{3\alpha}{2}$ and $\angle BAC = \alpha,$ we have $\angle ABD = \angle BAC + \angle ABC,$ so $AB = AD = 10.$  Then $AC = 2AD = 20.$

