We have the equations \begin{align*}
n-3+3+n+1&=2n-9+2+n-1+n-1\\
\Rightarrow\qquad 2n+1&=4n-12\\
\Rightarrow\qquad 13&=2n\\
\Rightarrow\qquad n&=\boxed{\frac{13}{2}}.
\end{align*}

